<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub527424_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="创作背景" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">冷雨夜</span>创作背景</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">歌曲是黄家驹作的曲，不过写出来后觉得太过“流行”，与他们当时的摇滚风格不相符，所以想扔掉。后来黄家强把它捡回来并且很欣赏，家驹就说：“那你自己填词自己唱吧”。这是首“命大”的歌。<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="《冷雨夜》歌曲相关图片"  href="/pic/%E5%86%B7%E9%9B%A8%E5%A4%9C/9469784/16821046/8640bf8b86c6d82e9e2fb4c7?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:159px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:157px;height:220px;">
<img class="picture" alt="《冷雨夜》歌曲相关图片" src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=d7982b6e8794a4c20e23e0293ef41bac/b64543a98226cffc1f0775d3b9014a90f603eaa6.jpg" style="width:157px;height:220px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
《冷雨夜》歌曲相关图片<span class="number">(4张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:151px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:145px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">家强当年为了音乐事业、Beyond乐队的发展，与他的女友分手，于是他填下《冷雨夜》的词，表达了他与女友分手后内心的苦楚。从中也可以看出家强对音乐、对Beyond的热爱的精神。<sup>[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_527424">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub527424_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="歌曲歌词" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">冷雨夜</span>歌曲歌词</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在雨中漫步</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">蓝色街灯渐露</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">相对望</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">无声紧拥抱着</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">为了找往日</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">寻温馨的往日</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">消失了</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">任雨洒我面</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">难分水点泪痕</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">心更乱</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">愁丝绕千百段</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">骤变的态度</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">无心伤她说话</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">收不了</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">冷雨夜我在你身边</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">盼望你会知</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">可知道我的心</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">比当初已改变</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">只牵强地相处</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">冷雨夜我不想归家</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">怕望你背影</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">只苦笑望雨点</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">须知要说清楚</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">可惜我没胆试</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在雨中漫步</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">尝水中的味道</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">仿似是</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">情此刻的尽时</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">未了解结合</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">留低思忆片段</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">不经意</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">冷雨夜我在你身边</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">盼望你会知</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">可知道我的心</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">比当初已改变</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">只牵强地相处</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">冷雨夜我不想归家</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">怕望你背影</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">只苦笑望雨点</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">须知要说清楚</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">可惜我没胆试<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="黄家强及Beyond"  href="/pic/%E5%86%B7%E9%9B%A8%E5%A4%9C/9469784/16567205/0b7b02087bf40ad134bd38d2532c11dfa9eccea2?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:147px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:145px;height:220px;">
<img class="picture" alt="黄家强及Beyond" src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=1d9f31ecaf64034f0bcdc5049fc37980/0b7b02087bf40ad134bd38d2532c11dfa9eccea2.jpg" style="width:145px;height:220px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
黄家强及Beyond<span class="number">(2张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:139px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:133px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">冷雨夜我在你身边</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">盼望你会知</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">可知道我的心</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">比当初已改变</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">只牵强地相处</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">冷雨夜我不想归家</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">怕望你背影</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">只苦笑望雨点</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">须知要说清楚</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">可惜我没胆试</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Wo…</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">Wo…<sup>[4]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[4]_527424">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub527424_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="歌曲鉴赏" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">冷雨夜</span>歌曲鉴赏</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">《冷雨夜》是Beyond乐队为数不多的情歌中的经典之一，也是黄家强在Beyond乐队主唱的歌曲中最经典的一首。<sup>[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_527424">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">整首歌的旋律都是很忧伤、凄凉、无奈的感觉；尤其是中间的Solo<sup>[2]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2]_527424">&nbsp;</a>
<i>（1991年Beyond生命接触演唱会）</i>、更是耐人寻味、堪称经典。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">这首家驹兄弟俩创作的情歌，开创了Beyond慢板情歌的先河。这情歌是与众不同的，都是怨曲风格，词、曲写得很有深度，像一杯陈年老酒，需要慢慢的品味。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="4" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub527424_4" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="重要演出" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">冷雨夜</span>重要演出</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">在1991年Beyond生命接触演唱会上，黄家强演奏的长达一分多钟的Bass Solo更是集技巧和情感于一体，耐人寻味，堪称经典，是<a target=_blank href="/item/Bass">Bass</a>爱好者最喜欢挑战的Solo之一。<sup>[2]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2]_527424">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%86%B7%E9%9B%A8%E5%A4%9C/9469784/0/5ab5c9ea15ce36d39429a7133df33a87e950b1e7?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="家强在演唱《冷雨夜》时的solo（截图）" style="width:220px;height:165px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="http://b.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=163c00ccaeec8a13101a50e2c7039157/5ab5c9ea15ce36d39429a7133df33a87e950b1e7.jpg"  alt="家强在演唱《冷雨夜》时的solo（截图）" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
家强在演唱《冷雨夜》时的solo（截图）
</span>
</div></div>
